import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <footer>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col className='text-center py-3'>
                        Copyright © by
                        <Link to={''}>
                            Thuận Trần
                        </Link>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        </footer>
    )
}

export default Footer
